<subSubSection id="6D0D10758373A638B041899BA02966E1" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph id="9728AFF35CDD27B4088A976265E20465" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0704C76DC607F26936949A7F72B1A57B" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<bibRefCitation id="4091F27C84D84A77B7C7CB6353CB485E" author="Habu, A" journalOrPublisher="Kontyu" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="257 - 259" refId="B13" refString="Habu, A, 1959. One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Kontyu 27: 257 - 259" title="One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae)." volume="27" year="1959">Habu (1959)</bibRefCitation>
describes 
<taxonomicName id="6B1D34D5951D3212DDF06F26E6B16342" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai" subGenus="Peryphus">Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai</taxonomicName>
from Hokkaido, Japan, reporting that the species is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="2BB0D9292DA8514C957070439586E72E" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus) amurense subsp. trajectum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="amurense" subGenus="Peryphus" subSpecies="trajectum">Bembidion (Peryphus) amurense trajectum</taxonomicName>
Netolitzky, 1939 (currently listed in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="45312B7FBF4DE77FFA506597C8438359" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
). Later, the species was listed in 
<bibRefCitation id="83ABE031B51EE19002BD315010847752" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Apollo Books, Stenstrup" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B28" refString="Marggi, W, Huber, C, Mueller-Motzfeld, G, Hartmann, M, 2003. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242-273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Apollo Books, Stenstrup" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242 - 273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2003">Marggi et al. (2003)</bibRefCitation>
in two different positions, within the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="14D0EB8938A6027A171C8B82238E65E4" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Ocydromus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ocydromus">Bembidion Ocydromus</taxonomicName>
but with the incorrect spelling 
<emphasis id="81788C67BA5EB9F1C4FF8FA607CD8B6F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">umeayi</emphasis>
(sic!) and within 
<taxonomicName id="CDEF184AED8673DE40CA8E8CAD037395" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="672640624ACA0BC5CD8E0AF1BE289439" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;incertae sedis&quot; with the correct name &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="E8A1CBA33127FB1EBC9AE49BBE56AADA" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai">
<emphasis id="54157CCA1E4C2AB2C3BDD6D07708FE70" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion umeyai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;. The same mistake, reported to us by our colleague Katsuyuki Terada (Hiroshima), also occurs in 
<bibRefCitation id="6999D3CF485E4FF7F6F1B4204F91E31F" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B29" refString="Marggi, W, Toledano, L, Neri, P, 2017. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294-342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Brill, Leiden" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294 - 342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2017">Marggi et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
. In 
<bibRefCitation id="E61EC229CEC56790B0B722C384F11C81" author="Habu, A" journalOrPublisher="Kontyu" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="257 - 259" refId="B13" refString="Habu, A, 1959. One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Kontyu 27: 257 - 259" title="One new species of Bembidion from Hokkaido (Coleoptera, Carabidae)." volume="27" year="1959">
<normalizedToken id="39E5AE45526076A6D997A7C211851DFD" originalValue="Habu’s">Habu's</normalizedToken>
(1959)
</bibRefCitation>
original description and in 
<bibRefCitation id="30029CAFB9105E23123790FD7AEEAF8A" author="Morita, S" journalOrPublisher="Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B31" refString="Morita, S, 2001. On Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai Habu: 293-296. Papers on Coleoptera in honor of Toshifumi Hozumi. The Coleopteran Fauna of Tokai District." title="On Bembidion (Peryphus) umeyai Habu: 293 - 296. Papers on Coleoptera in honor of Toshifumi Hozumi. The Coleopteran Fauna of Tokai District." year="2001">Morita (2001)</bibRefCitation>
the illustration of the aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName id="1F54DBFF7742DFB185F7447651D41CEE" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion umeyai" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="umeyai">
<emphasis id="DC2B0EACCE5DFA33500AC188C93C4140" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion umeyai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shows that the species belongs to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="EA416151C43D34DFE5CE054041917B16" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Politophanes)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Politophanes">Bembidion Politophanes</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
